msg":"&quot;12.1.2 When four pilots are boarded, the maximum FDP that may be scheduled <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">is 18 hours regardless of considerations </span></span>of acclimatisation or time of start of the FDP. Bunks shall be provided for the Flight Crew members not at the controls. The division of duty and In-Flight Relief must be kept in balance according to operational circumstances and no Flight Crew member will receive less than 3 hours&rsquo; total In-Flight Relief, which need not be continuous.&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cad.gov.hk/english/pdf/CAD371.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cad.gov.hk%2Fenglish%2Fpdf%2FCAD371.pdf&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8kcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=cc0627e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cad.gov.hk/english/pdf/CAD371.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n因航直飛Boston 要16 個鐘已經係接近用盡左extended FDP for Long Range Operation<br />\n呢個已經係計到盡<br />\n如果delay就一定要轉crew"},{"pid":"4ee3b190b7ebe15a406250de6e4b119569f39ad6","tid":1105452,"uid":199145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6de6466be65519129d4771922d97dc0669047540","tid":1105452,"uid":154222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"點解唔直飛Boston <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:39:58.000Z","msg":"咪就係直飛點知delay搞到pilot個duty cycle爆鐘逼住轉crew<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}